  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a pan and add cumin seeds, paprika powder, and red pepper flakes. Stir-fry for about 30 seconds.",
    "Add onions and garlic to the pan. Sauté until the onions are translucent.",
    "Crush tomatoes into chunks and add them to the pan with their juices. Let it simmer for a few minutes.",
    "Stir in beef stock cubes, water or vegan milk, and mix well. Bring it to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low and let the mixture cook for about 10-15 minutes until it starts to thicken slightly.",
    "Fold in cheese shreds and nutritional yeast. Stir until the cheese melts into the sauce.",
    "Serve immediately as an energizing snack or accompaniment to a light meal."
  ],
